## 🔧 Autonomy Modes

Try different autonomy modes to see how AI behavior changes:

- **Safe Mode** (`/mode safe`): AI asks for approval before making changes
- **Autonomous Mode** (`/mode autonomous`): AI automatically fixes code issues
- **Full Mode** (`/mode full`): Maximum autonomy with safety checks

